---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="特定商取引法に基づく表記 | RefineFlow Works"
  description="特定商取引法に基づく表記ページ"
>
<style>
  /* ── Nav ── */
  #nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    height: 60px; padding: 0 3rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 85%, transparent);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(180%);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px) saturate(180%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 15px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px;
  }
  .nav-logo-text {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg,
      #3b82f6 0%, #60a5fa 18%, #93c5fd 35%, #bfdbfe 50%,
      #93c5fd 65%, #60a5fa 82%, #3b82f6 100%);
    background-size: 280% 100%;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    color: transparent;
    animation: logoFlow 7s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) { #nav { padding: 0 1.5rem; } }

  /* ── Main ── */
  main {
    max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 100px 3rem 96px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) { main { padding: 88px 1.5rem 64px; } }

  /* ── Page header ── */
  .page-header { margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .page-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif), var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 40px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--fg);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--fg-3);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* ── Table ── */
  .legal-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
  }
  .legal-table tr {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .legal-table tr:first-child {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .legal-table th {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-3);
    font-weight: 400;
    text-align: left;
    padding: 1.4rem 2rem 1.4rem 0;
    width: 200px;
    vertical-align: top;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .legal-table td {
    padding: 1.4rem 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--fg-2);
    line-height: 1.9;
  }
  .legal-table a {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .legal-table a:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent-bright);
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .legal-table, .legal-table tbody, .legal-table tr,
    .legal-table th, .legal-table td {
      display: block;
    }
    .legal-table tr { padding: 1.25rem 0; }
    .legal-table tr:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .legal-table th {
      width: auto;
      padding: 0 0 0.3rem 0;
      white-space: normal;
    }
    .legal-table td { padding: 0; }
  }

  /* ── Note ── */
  .legal-note {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--fg-3);
    line-height: 1.9;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  /* ── Footer ── */
  footer {
    max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .footer-logo {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px;
  }
  .footer-logo-text {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6 0%, #60a5fa 50%, #3b82f6 100%);
    background-size: 200% 100%;
    -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; color: transparent;
    animation: logoFlow 7s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .footer-copy { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--fg-3); }
  .footer-back-wrap {
    max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 3rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .footer-back {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; color: var(--fg-3);
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.35rem;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .footer-back:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    footer { padding: 1.5rem; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .footer-back-wrap { padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; }
  }
</style>

<!-- Nav -->
<nav id="nav">
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 128 128" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink:0">
      <rect width="128" height="128" rx="26" fill="#0d1829"/>
      <rect x="8" y="24" width="12" height="80" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <rect x="8" y="24" width="50" height="12" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <rect x="46" y="24" width="12" height="36" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <rect x="8" y="48" width="50" height="12" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <polygon points="36,60 48,60 58,104 46,104" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <rect x="68" y="24" width="12" height="80" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <rect x="68" y="24" width="50" height="12" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <rect x="68" y="56" width="38" height="12" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
    </svg>
    <span class="nav-logo-text">RefineFlow Works</span>
  </a>
  <button id="lang-toggle" class="lang-toggle" aria-label="言語切り替え / Language">
    <span class="lt-ja">JP</span>
    <span class="lt-sep">/</span>
    <span class="lt-en">EN</span>
  </button>
</nav>

<!-- Main content -->
<main>
  <header class="page-header reveal">
    <span class="page-eyebrow">Legal</span>
    <h1 class="page-title">
      <span class="t-ja">特定商取引法に基づく表記</span>
      <span class="t-en">Legal Notice</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Specified Commercial Transactions Act</p>
  </header>

  <table class="legal-table">
    <tbody>
      <tr class="reveal" data-delay="0.05">
        <th><span class="t-ja">販売事業者</span><span class="t-en">Seller</span></th>
        <td>RefineFlow Works</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="reveal" data-delay="0.1">
        <th><span class="t-ja">代表者</span><span class="t-en">Representative</span></th>
        <td>
          <span class="t-ja">請求があった場合、遅滞なく開示いたします</span>
          <span class="t-en">Will be disclosed promptly upon request</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="reveal" data-delay="0.15">
        <th><span class="t-ja">所在地</span><span class="t-en">Address</span></th>
        <td>
          <span class="t-ja">〒107-0061<br/>東京都港区北青山1-3-3 三橋ビル 3階</span>
          <span class="t-en">Mitsuhashi Bldg. 3F, 1-3-3 Kitaaoyama,<br/>Minato-ku, Tokyo 107-0061, Japan</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="reveal" data-delay="0.2">
        <th><span class="t-ja">電話番号</span><span class="t-en">Phone</span></th>
        <td>
          <span class="t-ja">請求があった場合、遅滞なく開示いたします</span>
          <span class="t-en">Will be disclosed promptly upon request</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="reveal" data-delay="0.25">
        <th><span class="t-ja">メールアドレス</span><span class="t-en">Email</span></th>
        <td><a href="mailto:refineflow.works@gmail.com">refineflow.works@gmail.com</a></td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="reveal" data-delay="0.3">
        <th><span class="t-ja">販売価格</span><span class="t-en">Pricing</span></th>
        <td>
          <span class="t-ja">各サービス・プロダクトのページに記載、または個別見積による</span>
          <span class="t-en">Listed on each service/product page, or by individual quote</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="reveal" data-delay="0.35">
        <th><span class="t-ja">支払方法</span><span class="t-en">Payment Method</span></th>
        <td>
          <span class="t-ja">銀行振込、各種プラットフォーム（App Store / Google Play）の決済に準拠</span>
          <span class="t-en">Bank transfer, or in accordance with platform payment methods (App Store / Google Play)</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="reveal" data-delay="0.4">
        <th><span class="t-ja">支払時期</span><span class="t-en">Payment Terms</span></th>
        <td>
          <span class="t-ja">請求書発行日から30日以内、またはプラットフォームの規約に準拠</span>
          <span class="t-en">Within 30 days of invoice date, or in accordance with platform terms</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="reveal" data-delay="0.45">
        <th><span class="t-ja">商品の引渡時期</span><span class="t-en">Delivery</span></th>
        <td>
          <span class="t-ja">受託開発：契約締結後、別途協議の上定める期日<br/>アプリ・デジタル商品：購入手続き完了後、ただちに提供</span>
          <span class="t-en">Contract dev: By the date agreed upon after contract signing<br/>App / digital products: Provided immediately upon purchase</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="reveal" data-delay="0.5">
        <th><span class="t-ja">返品・キャンセル</span><span class="t-en">Returns & Cancellations</span></th>
        <td>
          <span class="t-ja">受託開発：業務着手前であればキャンセル可能。着手後は別途協議。<br/>デジタル商品：各プラットフォームの規約に準拠</span>
          <span class="t-en">Contract dev: Cancellable before work begins. After commencement, subject to negotiation.<br/>Digital products: Subject to platform terms</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="reveal" data-delay="0.55">
        <th><span class="t-ja">動作環境</span><span class="t-en">System Requirements</span></th>
        <td>
          <span class="t-ja">各アプリ・サービスのページに記載</span>
          <span class="t-en">Listed on each app/service page</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="reveal" data-delay="0.6">
        <th><span class="t-ja">その他</span><span class="t-en">Other</span></th>
        <td>
          <span class="t-ja">価格はすべて税込表示です。<br/>詳細はご契約時の個別合意書に準拠します。</span>
          <span class="t-en">All prices include tax.<br/>Details are subject to the individual agreement at the time of contract.</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="legal-note reveal" data-delay="0.65">
    <span class="t-ja">本ページに記載の内容は予告なく変更する場合があります。<br/>ご不明な点がございましたら <a href="mailto:refineflow.works@gmail.com">refineflow.works@gmail.com</a> までお問い合わせください。</span>
    <span class="t-en">The contents of this page are subject to change without notice.<br/>For inquiries, please contact <a href="mailto:refineflow.works@gmail.com">refineflow.works@gmail.com</a>.</span>
  </div>
</main>

<div class="footer-back-wrap">
  <a href="/" class="footer-back">
    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
      <polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/>
    </svg>
    Back
  </a>
</div>

<footer>
  <span class="footer-logo">
    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 128 128" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink:0">
      <rect width="128" height="128" rx="26" fill="#0d1829"/>
      <rect x="8" y="24" width="12" height="80" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <rect x="8" y="24" width="50" height="12" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <rect x="46" y="24" width="12" height="36" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <rect x="8" y="48" width="50" height="12" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <polygon points="36,60 48,60 58,104 46,104" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <rect x="68" y="24" width="12" height="80" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <rect x="68" y="24" width="50" height="12" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
      <rect x="68" y="56" width="38" height="12" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
    </svg>
    <span class="footer-logo-text">RefineFlow Works</span>
  </span>
  <span class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 RefineFlow Works All rights reserved.</span>
</footer>
</Layout>
